item.title: Cathedral Ceremony in Cheyenne, WY
item.description:
Cathedral Ceremony in Cheyenne, WY

In a beautiful cathedral in Cheyenne, Wyoming, this couple exchanged wedding vows and began their journey as husband and wife! The catholic ceremony was a joyous sacrament of marriage, starting with the bride and groom escorting each other down the aisle.

item.title: Larkspur Wedding: Memorable Toasts and Alternate Bouquet Toss
item.description:
Larkspur Wedding: Memorable Toasts and Alternate Bouquet Toss

Heather and Logan tied the knot on a sunny day in Larkspur, Colorado. An elegant outdoor ceremony exchanged vows, wove three strands into a cord to symbolize their union, and sealed their new marriage with a kiss!
